"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-07-25-paris-olympics-football-nothing-like-this-ever-happened-otamendi-reacts-as-morocco-beat-argentina\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Argentina captain to the 2024 Paris Olympics Games football events, Nicolas Otamendi has criticized the video assistant referee following his country's 2-1 defeat to Morocco.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 28, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999783995, \"rank\": 2.0924344220667787e-11, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 185, \"end\": 192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999265583, \"rank\": 7.335412396801134e-11, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was VAR's decision that led to La Albiceleste's defeat against Morocco in their opening group game.\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 297, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 202, \"end\": 205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.353848821617488e-27, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}, {\"begin\": 261, \"end\": 268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999265583, \"rank\": 7.335412396801134e-11, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The game, which ended in a 2-1 loss for Javier Mascherano's men at Geoffroy-Guichard Stadium in France, has left the South Americans devastated.\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 339, \"end\": 356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Javier Mascherano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\"}, {\"begin\": 395, \"end\": 401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999961346, \"rank\": 3.7557049005684684e-12, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morocco were 2-1 by the end of 90 minutes, which was followed by 15 minutes of injury time.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 445, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999265583, \"rank\": 7.335412396801134e-11, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Argentine midfielder, Cristian Medina netted what was to be a late equalizer but the game was interrupted following invasion of the pitch by angry Moroccan fans.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.50295896737428e-14, \