cco.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999265583, \"rank\": 7.335412396801134e-11, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Otamendi told reporters, \\\"It's a historic disgrace.\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing like this has ever happened before.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Morocco did not want to play, and neither did we.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1012, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999265583, \"rank\": 7.335412396801134e-11, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We waited for an hour and forty minutes, but no one told us anything.\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's frustrating because these are the Olympic Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Transfer: Smith Rowe to join Arsenal EPL rivals in \\u00a335million deal  Paris Olympics football: It's a disgrace - Mascherano reacts as Morocco beat Argentina 2-1  AFCON: CAF dividing Africa - Senegal's Gueye speaks on returning gold medals to Morocco  Moroccan club sack Senegal midfielder over AFCON 2025 title stripping remarks  'Senegal beat Morocco fair and square' - Rooney slams CAF over AFCON 2025 verdict  Senegal refuses to return AFCON trophy after CAF awards title to Morocco  AFCON: 'Corruption